    • Class it.uninsubria.shared.model.User

      class User extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • CF
          String CF
          Italian tax code (Codice Fiscale). Must be exactly 16 uppercase alphanumeric characters.
        • email
          String email
          User's email address. Must be unique across all users.
        • id
          String id
          Unique username for login. Minimum 5 characters, must contain at least one letter.
        • library
          List<Library> library
          List of personal libraries owned by this user.
        • name
          String name
          User's first name. Maximum 30 characters, no numbers allowed.
        • password
          String password
          Hashed password using BCrypt. Never stored in plain text.
        • profileImage
          byte[] profileImage
          Profile image stored as byte array. Supports various image formats.
        • profileImageType
          String profileImageType
          MIME type of the profile image. Examples: "image/png", "image/jpeg", "image/gif"
        • recoveryPhrase
          String recoveryPhrase
          Hashed recovery phrase for password reset functionality.
        • surname
          String surname
          User's last name. Maximum 30 characters, no numbers allowed.
        • user_id
          Integer user_id
          Database primary key for the user. Automatically generated as a serial number.
